Package: assertthat
Title: Easy Pre and Post Assertions
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: person("Hadley", "Wickham", , "hadley@rstudio.com", c("aut",
    "cre"))
Description: An extension to stopifnot() that makes it easy to declare
    the pre and post conditions that you code should satisfy, while
    also producing friendly error messages so that your users know
    what's gone wrong.
